                  <summary><p>A multi-text manuscript containing two Śaiva works:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Civakkiyāṉapōtakam</title>, that is, the <title xml:lang="ta">Civañāṉapōtakam</title>, text and commentary (U5).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Civakkiyāṉacittiyār</title>, that is, the <title xml:lang="ta">Civañāṉacittiyār Cupaṭcam</title>, text and commentary (U6).</item>
</list></p>
<p>Each of the texts has its own table(s) of contents:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Civañāṉapōtakam</title>, table of contents (<foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign>s) (U3).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Civañāṉapōtakam</title>, table of contents (<foreign xml:lang="ta">kāraṇam</foreign>s) (U4).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Civañāṉacittiyār Cupaṭcam</title>, table of contents (U7).</item>
</list></p>
   <p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (September 2021).</p>  <p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      </summary>
                  
